_sText:
Port from CS: Condition Zero. 
Remaster of my old port - of classic CS:CZ map...

Known Issues
some holes and problem areas (black brushes)

Note
Unfortunately, when I ported this map (around 2020) I was using the MBSPC decompiler. There was no better decompiler at that time, so I made many corrections manually, optimized the map. Now the state of the port is not bad, I would say mediocre, but nonetheless playable and looks good in many ways.
